<CELL ROLE="label"><HI>l.</HI></CELL>
<CELL ROLE="label"><HI>s.</HI></CELL>
<CELL ROLE="label"><HI>d.</HI></CELL>
</ROW>
<ROW>
<CELL>This ought by the Malt De|bentures
to draw back after the
rate of 4<HI>s.</HI> Sterling <HI>per</HI> Quar|ter,
which is in the whole</CELL>
