<ROW>
<CELL>And for the Bounty allow'd
by Act of Parliament, on the
Exportation of it as Corn, it
ought to receive al&s;o 2<HI>s.</HI> 6<HI>d.
per</HI> Quarter more, which is up|on
the whole</CELL>
